OL,3,CFirst Scottish Parliament election
OL,4,Cresults in our region expected soon
OL,6,FOliver Wright reports from the
OL,7,Felection count in Kelso.
OL,9,FResults from the Scottish Parliament
OL,10,Felection are starting to be declared,
OL,11,Fwith the first in our region expected
OL,12,Fsoon.
OL,14,FIn the South of Scotland, voters will
OL,15,Felect representatives to four
OL,16,Fconstituencies, as well as an
OL,17,Fadditional seven MSPs to represent the
OL,18,FSouth Scotland region.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
