OL,3,CFirst Scottish Parliament election
OL,4,Cresults in our region expected soon
OL,6,FIn the Borders, the two constituencies
OL,7,Fare Ettrick, Roxburgh and
OL,8,FBerwickshire, and Midlothian South
OL,9,FTweeddale and Lauderdale.
OL,11,FIn Dumfries and Galloway, the two
OL,12,Fconstituencies up for grabs are
OL,13,FDumfriesshire, and Galloway and West
OL,14,FDumfries.
OL,16,FThe results will be published on this
OL,17,Fpage as soon as they are announced.
OL,19,FLive results
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
