OL,3,CFirst Scottish Parliament election
OL,4,Cresults in our region expected soon
OL,6,FTurnout down in Dumfriesshire and
OL,7,FGalloway and West Dumfries
OL,9,FTurnout figures for two constituencies
OL,10,Fhave been revealed.
OL,12,FIn Dumfriesshire, 51.7% of the
OL,13,Felectorate voted - down from 66% in
OL,14,F2021.
OL,16,FIn the Galloway and West Dumfries
OL,17,Fconstituency, turnout in 2026 was
OL,18,F51.9% - down from 64.9% in 2021.
